Download Android studio
==========================

https://developer.android.com/studio/

Create project in android studio:
-----------------------------------

  -  Open android studio
  -  select "start new android stuidio project"
  -  give application name
  -  package name should be unique.
  -  Better to select api15 as android sdk version.
  -  select empty activity.
  - click finish
  - Project will be created.


Folder Structure:
-------------

app  - code
  manifests
     - androidmanifests.xml  ->contains basic details about the app.
  java  - business logic code
    - MainActivity -> start point of the application.
  res -> contains icons, music , images
    - drawable
    - layout
        - activity_main.xml  (home page of app) [ controls the layout of the application]
    - mipmap
    - values

gradle ( automated build tool)


Add componenents into the application:
---------------------------------------

Drag and drop the componeents into the application.
use relative layout.
To change the layout from constraintlayout to relativelayout , right the constraintlayout in the componeent tree and select convert and
select relativelayout.
